title: Pasta Fagioli
directions: Drain fat from beef and add to crock pot with everything except pasta.
Cook on low 7-8 hours or high 4-5 hours. Add pasta the last 30 minutes.
Serve with a nice crisp green salad and some garlic bread!
ingredients: Pasta Fagioli in the Crockpot~ just like Olive Garden
1 (16 ounce) can red kidney beans, drained
1 (16 ounce) can white kidney beans, drained
